sentences: The SBSTA adopted conclusions and recommended draft CMP conclusions (FCCC/SBSTA/2013/L.24 and Add.1).

Clarification of text in section G, Protocol Article 3.7 ter of the Doha Amendment to the Protocol: Facilitator Nagmeldin Elhassan (Sudan) reported that the informal group was unable to complete work on this issue but had agreed to invite the CMP to consider these issues further with a view to adopting a decision at this session.
The SBSTA adopted conclusions reflecting this (FCCC/SBSTA/2013/L.31).
